The hypothesis is
that life on Earth

00:30:12.290 --> 00:30:14.790
has emerged in part
deterministically

00:30:14.790 --> 00:30:17.050
from the laws of
chemistry and physics

00:30:17.050 --> 00:30:20.310
but also evolution
by natural selection

00:30:20.310 --> 00:30:24.504
to maximize organismal
power, given the constraints

00:30:24.504 --> 00:30:25.295
