00:30:32.964 --> 00:30:34.380
So what I would
like to do is work

00:30:34.380 --> 00:30:37.610
through several
different examples, what

00:30:37.610 --> 00:30:39.390
appear to be very
deterministic, very

00:30:39.390 --> 00:30:43.050
rule-like aspects of biology.

00:30:43.050 --> 00:30:47.716
The first is something known
as the citric acid cycle.

00:30:47.716 --> 00:30:49.215
It's a part of your
core metabolism.

00:30:53.530 --> 00:30:55.510
So when you take
introductory biology,

00:30:55.510 --> 00:30:57.910
