00:36:48.910 --> 00:36:52.557
as well, again, some basic
building blocks of life.

00:36:52.557 --> 00:36:54.390
So very interesting,
you can run it forward,

00:36:54.390 --> 00:36:55.590
you can run it backwards.

00:36:55.590 --> 00:36:58.250
And depending on the
local environment,

00:36:58.250 --> 00:37:00.027
that would then select
for whether or not

00:37:00.027 --> 00:37:01.735
you're running this
forward or backwards.

