00:42:05.150 --> 00:42:07.850
probably provide
beneficial associations,

00:42:07.850 --> 00:42:10.740
so much so that the
fact that now, you're

00:42:10.740 --> 00:42:13.750
organelles within your
cells appear ultimately

00:42:13.750 --> 00:42:17.910
to be traced back to these
